Download logo The Minister of Foreign Affairs, H.E. Dr. Abdullatif bin Rashid Al Zayani, received in his office today the Ambassador of the People's Democratic Republic of Algeria to the Kingdom of Bahrain, H.E. Abdelhamid Ahmed Khoja.  The two sides discussed the strong brotherly relations linking the Kingdom of Bahrain and the brotherly People's Democratic Republic of Algeria, and reviewed ways to further enhance bilateral cooperation and coordination in various fields to meet common interests. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Kingdom of Bahrain.